Parameter Detail

outf

This is the prefix of the filename where the graph is saved. The extension is ".gml" and after the prefix the basename contains a numeric index that is incremented at each saving point. If not given, the graph is dumped on the standard output.

dht

This is the reference to the DHT Protocol. DHTProtocol
